OL,4,CUN human rights chief calls for
OL,5,Creparations over racism
OL,6, The United Nations Human Rights Council
OL,7, has urged global action including
OL,8, reparations to "make amends" for racism
OL,9, against people of African descent.
OL,11,FIts new report also urges educational
OL,12,Freform and apologies to address
OL,13,Fdiscrimination.
OL,15,FThe findings cite concerns in about 60
OL,16,Fcountries including the UK, Belgium,
OL,17,FFrance, Canada, Brazil and Colombia.
OL,19,FThe study began after the murder of
OL,20,FGeorge Floyd, an unarmed black man, in
OL,21,FUS police custody in 2020.
